    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1866-12-08T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1866-12-08T00:00:00-05:00" n="66" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d66">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Hale</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                                Seward</persName>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 70.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Agency and Consulate General U. S.
                                        of America</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Alexandria,
                                    Egypt,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1866-12-08">
                            <hi rend="italic">December</hi> 8, 1866</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir :</hi> Your telegram, in answer to mine of the
                            27th ultimo, was received last evening, the circuit of 12,000 miles
                            having been completed in 10 days, notwithstanding the break in the wire
                            between this place and Malta, which required my message to go thither by
                            steamer, and delayed the prompt transmission thence of yours. The break
                            was repaired yesterday.</p>
                <p>Surratt remains in safe custody, and subject to no jurisdiction other
                            than that of the United States.</p>
                <p>I have the honor to be, sir, very respectfully, your obedient
                            servant,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>CHARLES HALE.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>Hon. <hi rend="smallcaps">William H. Seward</hi>
                        <hi rend="italic">Secretary of State, Washington, D. C.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
